com.example.trialio.controllers

Class QuestionForumManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.trialio.controllers.QuestionForumManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class QuestionForumManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    QuestionForumManager manages Question and Reply Posts for an experiment and is responsible for the persistence of Post data. This class is used to perform create, read, update and delete functionality on questions and replies that are to be stored for an experiment. This class communicates with the Firebase database.
